  "text": "The BUT test, however, requires specific equipment built for this purpose; there is no such device manufacturer. Other authors like Darendeliler et al. [CITATION_1] used the simulation program to evaluate the COF through simpler techniques, such as tribological tests only in the sheets, like the pin-on-disk test.",
